Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:14.15,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurasara,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:20.04,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a spell on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:24.79,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:26.56,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:27.67,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.50,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a magic song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.90,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Ishigata-san taught it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.15,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,He says it cheers you up if you \Nsing it when you're lonely or hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.47,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyoko, want to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:39.47,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.23,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.26,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:53.19,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:54.97,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.57,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.76,0:01:00.11,Punchline-Flashback,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:05.99,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Guriko,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:09.23,Punchline-Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,let's run away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.69,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Pine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.34,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,You know we can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.45,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,There's an electrified fence all around the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.45,0:01:16.99,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,and besides—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:19.85,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,So you're okay with how things are, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.35,Punchline-Flashback,Pine,0000,0000,0000,,Trapped here for your whole life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:26.97,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:30.69,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's talk to Ishigata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.75,Punchline-Flashback,Guriko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.20,Punchline-Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Punch Line
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:16.55,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Gliese-sama is an alien from \Nthe planet Gliese 832C.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:19.55,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura, are you sane?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:20.67,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.70,Punchline-Ep_Title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Possessed by the Stripes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.44,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly sane.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:29.43,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,So, this Gliese person is coming to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:30.86,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.19,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:36.79,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, can you hold on to this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:38.44,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:43.28,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,He might think I'm a weirdo if \NI have this doll in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.25,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.91,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wait—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.75,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,And what the heck is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.81,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Early this morning, \Na young woman was found
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.50,Punchline-Meiko_Shouro,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Shouro Meiko-san (17)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.50,Punchline-News_Low,Text,0000,0000,0000,,High school student falls from apartment building
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:58.50,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}collapsed and bleeding at \Nher apartment premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.69,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,She was soon confirmed dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.14,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,A,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased was identified \Nas Shouro Meiko-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:04.65,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,a local high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:06.35,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Shouro Meiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:11.13,Punchline-Names,,0000,0000,0000,,Koto Monami (17)\N\NShouro Meiko (17)\N\NIo Ruka (17)\N\NHikiotani Ito (17)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:09.00,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't she in that video?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.93,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.96,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's a list of all the people they're going to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.10,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,A notice of premeditated crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.66,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,That means Ito's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:24.22,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Ito doesn't seem to know about this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.19,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell her, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:33.21,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,The quickest way would be \Nto possess someone's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.13,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.13,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard anything about possessing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.09,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Because I never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.59,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possess someone until \Nyou reach a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.97,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there are a few rules \Nfor possessing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.69,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.61,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:53.79,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.54,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}Ba-dum! Girls Everywhere Swim Meet{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.32,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:01.86,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.78,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.99,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Possession rule number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.07,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,If the owner of the body is lucid \Nwhile they are being possessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the possessor must have high spirit \Npower in order to possess them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.99,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,So I just need to use cinnamon \Nto increase my spirit power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.82,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Possession rule number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.95,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Fundamentally, it's only possible \Nto possess someone with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a similar spiritual wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:29.55,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Provided, however, that the owner of \Nthe body has spirit medium potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.37,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit medium potential?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:37.99,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Go scatter some cinnamon, \Nand possess Rabura's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:43.36,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Meika, about this email \Nfrom that Gliese person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.14,Punchline-Top,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:46.95,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got that email, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.16,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.91,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to ask him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.66,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Well, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:57.80,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the cinnamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.04,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Is it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.13,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:08.40,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Now to figure out how to bring Rabura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.25,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,All right, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:12.18,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Rabura's place, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.23,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.93,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that guy sure is thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:19.94,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously. I wouldn't be so \Nroundabout if I were him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:16.93,Punchline-Top,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:27.53,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.48,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.79,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, I'm busy right now. Save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.54,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening-ning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:37.72,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:43.25,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.09,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:50.68,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.47,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.58,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I have to possess her fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.55,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Forget the excuses. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:59.16,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I didn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.16,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.26,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.57,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.03,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,"Work"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.09,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Ito, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.09,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:17.49,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.87,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's seriously bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.37,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.50,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What is?! I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.23,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Rabura-san, you're acting a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:26.92,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.75,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,The way you're talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:31.05,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,You sound different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:35.59,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, they won't believe me \Nno matter how I explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:37.31,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.54,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh me, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.68,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.23,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.64,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, there's \Nsomething I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.32,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,See—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.86,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:51.08,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,First, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.22,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:55.85,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was wondering, \Nwhat's your favorite flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.33,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:01.53,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite flower... My favorite flower, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.45,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Rafflesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.91,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I have a question, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:07.52,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.36,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.22,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:13.29,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.64,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,That song about "your buns," or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.60,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,The She's Mei one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:20.83,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:24.40,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,You listen to our music!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.70,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,The last question's from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.29,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.28,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What snacks do you like with your beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.91,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.28,Punchline-Turtle_Feed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle Feed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.28,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.24,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Turtle feed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:43.01,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You're done now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.40,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.96,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.24,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.32,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.55,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?! Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.52,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rabura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.18,Punchline-Level_Up,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Bewitching Spirit Wave
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:06.60,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:11.96,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, you can only possess \Nsomeone for up to seven minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.19,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.20,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,That's a unique dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:22.24,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.78,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,My, you flatterer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.17,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, a toast to our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.67,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:35.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll go find some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.55,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.37,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:43.56,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you'll know once you try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.45,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I will, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:49.83,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.72,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I-It tastes rather different...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.88,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.61,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe because they just \Nrecently revamped the product.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:01.19,Punchline-Turtle_Feed,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Turtle Feed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:01.20,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.14,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.85,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:08.57,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I think my body was in shock \Nfrom how delicious it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.12,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:12.82,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:15.59,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm full now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.40,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:22.36,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Um, why don't I turn on some music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.39,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Then please, play this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:27.40,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,"I Want to See Your Buns"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.90,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.66,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I have this already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.11,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.63,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:39.52,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,It's your favorite song, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:42.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't exactly say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.51,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It is! It's my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.43,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I listen to it so much, I've worn out the disc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.92,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness I have another one now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.69,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I have one more very special present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.93,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.63,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.68,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:03.73,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,A rafflesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.81,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,You must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:07.37,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.19,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,No, it just has a very... unique scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:14.16,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's the scent of a dead animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:18.44,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Rafflesia attract flies with this scent \Nso they can spread their pollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.86,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see. Flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.44,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.12,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.32,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.33,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You're mocking me, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.34,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not my intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Then what {\i1}is{\i0} your intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:40.09,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to make you happy, Rabura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.95,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.11,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,With {\i1}this{\i0} flower?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.34,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,With turtle feed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.85,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.19,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:08.83,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I gave those answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:13.62,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what it said in \Nthe emails your friends sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:16.63,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.30,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,That does bring something to mind, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:20.95,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:25.89,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to have had a similar \Nexperience when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:30.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I was about five at the time, \Nso I don't remember too well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.89,Punchline-Timeline,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}24 Years Ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.89,Punchline-Top,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up in the middle of the \Nnight, and did strange things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:37.44,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Writing down diagrams and equations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and instructions on what \Nto do on certain dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:43.92,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,And I was sending them to someone by fax.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:49.56,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,So you think what happened here \Nwas another sleepwalking incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.27,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I apologize for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.08,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.66,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.94,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start over, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:07.39,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:12.18,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura-san, I can't stand to lie \Nto you any more than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:14.72,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.86,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.69,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't an alien, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.61,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.43,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I didn't come from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:30.27,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from the U.S. Department of \NDefense's intelligence bureau,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the National Security Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.53,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:49.43,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I trust that you know about the \NQmay Group hostage incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.95,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.57,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,And their announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:58.11,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Something about an asteroid hitting \NEarth on New Year's Eve or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:02.23,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,But the government and other\N experts said that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:08.42,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,No, unless Operation Intercept is \Ncarried out, it will collide with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:08.99,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.92,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,The United States has secretly \Nlaunched a military satellite into orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.92,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,equipped with several dozen nuclear missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:19.16,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,The satellite is under the command of the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air Force Space Command, also known as AFSPC.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:25.60,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,The goal of Operation Intercept \Nis to use these missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to destroy the incoming asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:32.33,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,But the Qmay Group uploaded \Na virus to the AFSPC servers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has taken over the entire system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.81,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,The Qmay Group did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:40.26,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Unless something is done, the AFSPC \Nmissiles will not be launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:44.98,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Their true objective has always been \Nthe annihilation of the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:46.86,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:50.13,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't the Qmay Group cause \Nthat incident to tell people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that the asteroid was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.99,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:59.02,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,The Qmay Group virus is very sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.79,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary person could not remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:06.51,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,But there is someone with genius \Nhacking skills who could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.30,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.63,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Daihatsu Meika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:16.24,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one else on Earth \Nwho could remove the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:21.27,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we've attempted to establish \Ncontact with her many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:21.84,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,but—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.46,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.32,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:33.63,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You thought you could get to \NMeika by getting close to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.62,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:37.47,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura-san, please don't misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I was attracted to you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.04,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.20,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to make me happy, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.58,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:49.26,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly is full of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:53.53,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:56.76,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I have a little something to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.02,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:00.79,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Is there atmosphere in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:01.72,Punchline-To_Rain,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Lose Not to Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.79,0:16:04.48,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear your thoughts on that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.86,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:21.15,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Special attack, Clam Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:37.10,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're \Ndoing to my Gliese-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.75,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:47.67,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Please, get away while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:49.62,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:52.33,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,He's really powerful when he wants to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.28,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,So please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.16,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.87,Default,Gliese,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repay this debt, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.87,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.52,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:05.37,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.02,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.75,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.76,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:17.44,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miya-Ken! We can trust him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.51,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Meika...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:22.37,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Now go. You need to chase \Nhim down, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:23.77,Default,Miyazawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.02,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? Wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.42,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.23,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Meika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:38.53,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.23,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:45.91,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:18:02.43,Default,Chiyoko,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is totally {\i1}Ba-dum! \NGirls Everywhere Swim Meet{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:06.57,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I want to see your buns
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.85,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.30,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:10.75,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Those plump, white buns
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.71,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:14.66,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A peek at your buns
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.05,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.95,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:21.10,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Takes me higher than Burj Khalifa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:22.53,Punchline-Internal/Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.16,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you get into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.63,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Meika was defending that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.85,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Miya-Ken, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.19,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:34.38,Default,Meika,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.59,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You're a robot. You wouldn't \Nunderstand how people feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.03,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Rabura-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:43.79,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What, did it not work out with that old dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.62,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,You stop it, too, Meika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.35,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get along, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.26,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Muhi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.81,Punchline-Legs,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Bare Legs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:54.62,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he's the \Nactual cause of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:57.03,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Because you brought that thing home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.65,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't just bring him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:00.47,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He was given to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.99,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,From Rabura's little brother, Rando-oniichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.39,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you bringing that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:10.38,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He came to my room all of \Na sudden about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:13.19,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted me to take \Ncare of this cub for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.02,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:18.68,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,This kid can be such a pathological liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.68,0:19:20.08,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Pathological liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:21.37,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.36,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Spirit mediums are all full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.81,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,You're so wimpy, you can't even \Ngo to school. You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.04,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.44,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.42,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.50,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,You were such good friends until yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.31,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.05,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't put up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.17,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I have to think some things over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:46.29,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's about a guy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.50,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I were as carefree as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.98,Default,Rabura,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to humanity doesn't \Nmean a thing to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.60,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.60,0:19:55.82,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is she on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.47,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:19:59.84,Default,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.61,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan, please forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.72,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Rabura-san and Meika both really—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.08,0:20:09.35,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you playing the nice girl for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.35,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to be a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.35,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:16.43,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ito-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:17.23,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:20.25,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me spell it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.79,Default,Ito,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hero, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.71,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.76,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:57.20,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Unbeijini nyopurasara...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:03.72,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put a spell on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.78,Default,Mika,0000,0000,0000,,Narugino, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:52.54,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:54.56,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:55.82,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:57.25,Default,Yuta,0000,0000,0000,,Ito!
